    <h3 class="section-title">Technical Specifications</h3>
    
    <div class="tech-section">
        <div class="tech-title">Recommended Technology Stack</div>
        
        <p><strong>Backend:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>API: Node.js with Express/Fastify or Python with Django/FastAPI</li>
            <li>Database: PostgreSQL for relational data, Redis for caching</li>
            <li>Authentication: JWT with OAuth 2.0</li>
            <li>File Storage: AWS S3 or similar cloud storage</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Frontend:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Framework: React.js with TypeScript</li>
            <li>State Management: Redux Toolkit or Zustand</li>
            <li>UI Components: Material-UI or Tailwind CSS</li>
            <li>Mobile: React Native or Flutter</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Infrastructure:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Cloud Provider: AWS, Google Cloud, or Azure</li>
            <li>Containerization: Docker with Kubernetes</li>
            <li>CI/CD: GitHub Actions or GitLab CI</li>
            <li>Monitoring: Prometheus, Grafana, Sentry</li>
        </ul>
